DESCRIPTION:An evening of clarinet music — Graduate Recital by Andrew Seohyeon Kim\, with Edward Holly at the piano.\n\nProgramme:\n• Sumin Park — Three Korean Folk Melodies about Bird\n• Robert Schumann — Fantasiestücke\, Op. 73\n• Johannes Brahms — Sonata for Clarinet and Piano No. 1 in F minor\, Op. 120 No. 1\n• SiHyun Uhm — Parents' Love
